INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("31","1","2014-06-27 04:41:36","2014-06-27 04:41:36","When you spend $20,000 on a kitchen you want a great finish, not a cheap look, you want “wow” factor, and that’s what Artra is all about.
But it’s more than that. At Artra we know kitchens, and we know that your kitchen is so much more than just a place to cook and eat…. It’s the place where your family gathers the most, where you watch your children grow as they sit at the bench eating breakfast, where you talk through the big decisions in life and celebrate your achievements. It’s the heart of your home, where all the magic happens…
Such an important part of your home should only be built by the best, and at Artra that’s what you will get, nothing but the best – the best quality materials and finishes, the best communication and the fairest prices, with professionalism and flexibility to custom-make your kitchen exactly how you envision. No restrictive sizes like you get through other companies.
Fresh and modern or classic wood, Artra has something for everyone, and when you build your kitchen with us you can be assured of quality craftsmanship and products that will last a lifetime.
Speak to our friendly, fully-qualified staff today about a style that suits your vision and budget, and we’ll give you a kitchen that gets everyone talking!","Full Width","","publish","closed","open","","full-width","","","2014-06-29 05:43:45","2014-06-29 05:43:45","","0","http://local.artra.com/?page_id=31","5","page","","0");
