INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("40","1","2014-06-27 04:57:08","2014-06-27 04:57:08","<h2>The smart choice in kitchens and cabinetry in Western Australia... Do it once. Do it right</h2>
The rare opportunity to build or renovate a kitchen is a chance to make a smart investment. Do it right, and your new kitchen can dramatically increase the value of your home (to the extent that the kitchen well-and-truly pays for itself, when it comes time to sell).
That’s why we specialise in kitchens and cabinets, done right. You won’t find any mass-produced doors or finicky, poor-fitting flat-packs here.
Instead, we craft custom designed, made-to-measure fittings, often using the finest Jarrah timber (our specialty).
Artra custom kitchens and cabinets strike the perfect balance between visual appeal and practicality (the keys to creating a ‘wow factor’ home or premises). Our craftsmanship is sure to breathe life into your renovated area and be a talking point for years to come.
<h2>Call us on 0488 441 910 or request a free quote now</h2>","Home","","publish","closed","open","","home","","","2014-06-29 17:19:11","2014-06-29 17:19:11","","0","http://local.artra.com/?page_id=40","1","page","","0");
