INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("106","1","2014-06-29 17:50:09","2014-06-29 17:50:09","<h2>“Wow” factor kitchens built to budget and size</h2>
When you spend $20,000 on a kitchen you want a great finish, not a cheap look, you want “wow” factor, and that’s what Artra is all about.
<h3>Heading 3</h3>
But it’s more than that. At Artra we know kitchens, and we know that your kitchen is so much more than just a place to cook and eat…. It’s the place where your family gathers the most, where you watch your children grow as they sit at the bench eating breakfast.
<h4>Heading 4</h4>
where you talk through the big decisions in life and celebrate your achievements. It’s the heart of your home, where all the magic happens…
<h5>Heading 5</h5>
Such an important part of your home should only be built by the best, and at Artra that’s what you will get, nothing but the best – the best quality materials and finishes, the best communication and the fairest prices, with professionalism and flexibility to custom-make your kitchen exactly how you envision. No restrictive sizes like you get through other companies.
<ul>
	<li>Fresh and modern or classic wood, Artra has something for everyone</li>
	<li>and when you build your kitchen with us you can be assured of quality</li>
	<li>craftsmanship and products that will last a lifetime.</li>
</ul>
<ol>
	<li>Speak to our friendly, fully-qualified staff today about a style that</li>
	<li>suits your vision and budget, and we’ll give you a kitchen that gets everyone talking!</li>
</ol>","Why Us","","inherit","closed","open","","7-revision-v1","","","2014-06-29 17:50:09","2014-06-29 17:50:09","","7","http://local.artra.com/7-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0");
INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("107","1","2014-06-29 17:51:19","2014-06-29 17:51:19","<h2>Heading 2 - “Wow” factor kitchens built to budget and size</h2>
